Invocation Name: keeping up
des:
Haunted houses, jealous neighbours, litigating kangaroos, little men from a chocolate factory and a family guy trying his best to balance wealth and happiness for his family!

Be part of oddball and funny situations that entertain you while also teaching you to be mindful of your personal financial habits.

Are you prepared to make some of the hardest decisions of your family life?

You live as the patriarch of a suburban American household, presented with an ever-expanding array of difficult choices. Make good choices and keep your family together as long as you can!

Write to us with your thoughts and feedback at - contact@thealexa.dev
